{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-445-retractions-a","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Changamoto 445: Kurudisha A","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Niz celih brojeva $S = \\{s_i\\}$ naziva se nizom dužine $n$ ako ima $n$ elemenata i svaki element $s_i$ zadovoljava $1 ≤ s_i ≤ n$. Ukupan broj različitih nizova dužine $n$ je $n^n$.</p>\n<p>$f_{n, a, b}(x) ≡ ax + b\\bmod n$ kwa $a, b, x$ nambari kamili na $0 \\lt a \\lt n$, $0 \\le b \\lt n$, $0 \\le x \\lt n$.</p>\n<p>Za bilo koji niz $S$, neka $L(S)$ predstavlja dužinu najdužeg uzastopnog podniza sa istim vrednostima. Na primer, za gore dati niz $S$, važi $L(S) = 3$, zbog tri uzastopne sedmice.</p>\n<p>Acha $R(n)$ iwe idadi ya kurudisha kwa $n$.</p>\n<p>Umepatiwa kwamba</p>\n<p>$$\\sum_{k = 1}^{99\\,999} R(\\displaystyle\\binom{100\\,000}{k}) \\equiv 628\\,701\\,600\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007$$</p>\n<p>Tafuta $$\\sum_{k = 1}^{9\\,999\\,999} R(\\displaystyle\\binom{10\\,000\\,000}{k})$$ Toa jibu lako modulo $1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f52a1000cf542c51003c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302117,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-445-retractions-a"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function retractionsA() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nretractionsA();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>retractionsA()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>659104042</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(retractionsA